.TH BCHART 1 "2026-04-23" "smartmet-monitor" "SmartMet Server"
.SH NAME
bchart \- btop\-style vertical chart of one access\-log metric
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B bchart
.RI [ \-i\  INTERVAL ]
.RI [ \-m\  reqs|ms|kb|mb|err ]
.RI [ \-h\  HEIGHT ]
.RI [ \-w\  CELLW ]
.RI [ LOG-FILE ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B bchart
renders a vertical Unicode block chart of a chosen metric over time.
Each column represents one time bucket; bar heights are auto\-scaled
to the maximum observed value and a y\-axis legend is printed on the
left.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-i \ INTERVAL
Time\-bucket width. One of
.BR 1s ,\  10s ,\  1m ,\  10m ,\  1h ,\  1d .
Default
.BR 1h .
.TP
.BI \-m \ METRIC
Metric to plot. One of
.BR reqs ,\  ms ,\  kb ,\  mb ,\  err :
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
.B reqs \- requests per bucket
.IP \(bu 2
.B ms   \- mean latency (ms)
.IP \(bu 2
.B kb   \- mean response size (KB)
.IP \(bu 2
.B mb   \- total bandwidth (MB)
.IP \(bu 2
.B err  \- error rate (%)
.RE
Default
.BR reqs .
.TP
.BI \-h \ HEIGHT
Chart height in rows. Default
.BR 12 .
.TP
.BI \-w \ CELLW
Columns per time bucket. Default
.BR 2 .
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR bstat (1),
.BR burls (1),
.BR bstatus (1),
.BR bkeys (1),
.BR smtop (1)
